Dmero-D, PCR & VHS

Na diagonal temos os histogramas, mostrando como cada varivel se distribu. Os risquinhos na parte de baixo indicam aonde cada observao se localiza. Nos painis superiores temos as correlaes, estrelas indicam significncia (trs estrelas significam p-valor < 0.0001). Nos painis inferiores temos os grficos de disperso num estilo mapa de calor para facilitar a visualizao, dado que temos muitas observaes. As retas em vermelho correspondem a modelos lineares para indicar a tendncia, em cinza seus intervalos de 95% de confiana.

Referncias

A anlise estatstica foi realizada no ambiente de computao estatstica R (R Core Team, 2022). Os principais pacotes R utilizados foram o {dplyr} (Wickham et al., 2022), {tidyr} (Wickham & Girlich, 2022), {forcats} (Wickham, 2021), {lubridate} (Grolemund & Wickham, 2011), {ggplot2} (Wickham, 2016), {patckwork} (Pedersen, 2020), {geobr} (Pereira & Gonalves, 2022), {psych} (Revelle, 2022), e {ggalluvial} (Brunson & Read, 2020).

R Core Team (2022). R: A language and environment for statistical computing. R Foundation for Statistical Computing, Vienna, Austria. URL https://www.R-project.org/

Wickham, H., Franois, R., Henry, L., Mller, K. (2022). dplyr: A Grammar of Data Manipulation. R package version 1.0.9. https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=dplyr

Wickham, H., Girlich, M. (2022). tidyr: Tidy Messy Data. R package version 1.2.0, https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=tidyr

Wickham, H. (2021). forcats: Tools for Working with Categorical Variables (Factors). R package version 0.5.1, https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=forcats

Grolemund, G., Wickham, H. (2011). Dates and Times Made Easy with lubridate. Journal of Statistical Software, 40(3), 1-25. https://www.jstatsoft.org/v40/i03/

Wickham, H. (2016). ggplot2: Elegant Graphics for Data Analysis. Springer-Verlag New York

Pedersen, T. L. (2020). patchwork: The Composer of Plots. R package version 1.1.1. https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=patchwork
